metadata.name: Chevel Studio Sound Collectibles #1
metadata.description:
Chevel Studio Sound Collectibles is a collation of recorded samples available on-chain exclusively on Zora - by Italian recording artist Dario Tronchin.

The sounds have been recorded, created and meticulously archived over the last ten years of studio practice.

These sounds are available for the first time as collectibles on-chain.

Collectors are allowed to use these sounds for the creation of commercial productions and NFTs with no limitations.
